fest” and I’ll send you my person guidebook on how I did this and manifested my dream life because of. 🤍 #manifestation #lawofdetachment", "duration": 40.47, "timestamp": 1772837159, "uploader_id": "275052411", "uploader": "Datrie", "channel": "datrie", "like_count": 206, "comment_count": 42, "comments": [{"author": "david.rintalan", "author_id": "48923281", "id": "18091380503275520", "text": "Manifest", "timestamp": 1773957309}, {"author": "orlandoavalon_", "author_id": "78440818280", "id": "18383167543090166", "text": "Manifest", "timestamp": 1773865239}, {"author": "naveen19193kumar", "author_id": "8625694751", "id": "17938368918175310", "text": "Manifest ❤️", "timestamp": 1773672096}, {"author": "superwkf", "author_id": "55373947245", "id": "18080098670364936", "text": "Manifest", "timestamp": 1773601906}, {"author": "quinn.tho", "author_id": "34506791669", "id": "18097418809956255", "text": "Manifest", "timestamp": 1773391062}], "thumbnails": [{"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/641264626_896451570040915_5107522303836797667_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi42NDB4MTEzNi5zZHIuZjcxODc4Lm5mcmFtZV9jb3Zlcl9mcmFtZS5jMiJ9&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=107&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gFusIKB_MqvtQv7JS4X9_815OJYbNWbfOZ3-t4t1lAIFV5cu0rL4YZwj-_9k22iF18&_nc_ohc=A8N4VbIgcHYQ7kNvwFAAO2C&_nc_gid=4eqKXJgXJFZcdG_3xoqdLw&edm=ANTKIIoBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af29l3hqXVZZywrtxzwSwSYNbQ9MVE7TIO3U8PLvZRiSVA&oe=69D4D18E&_nc_sid=d885a2", "width": 640, "height": 1136, "id": "0", "resolution": "640x1136"}, {"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/641264626_896451570040915_5107522303836797667_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi42NDB4MTEzNi5zZHIuZjcxODc4Lm5mcmFtZV9jb3Zlcl9mcmFtZS5jMiJ9&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=107&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gFusIKB_MqvtQv7JS4X9_815OJYbNWbfOZ3-t4t1lAIFV5cu0rL4YZwj-_9k22iF18&_nc_ohc=A8N4VbIgcHYQ7kNvwFAAO2C&_nc_gid=4eqKXJgXJFZcdG_3xoqdL